  "text": "2. Beacon sets with simple beacons. Even with simple beacons, our beacon placement solution reduces the beacon set sizes of [CITATION_1] by 40 − 70%. This suggests that it may be feasible to design a simpler monitoring infrastructure that does not require that network nodes use different transmission rules for probe packets.",
